Ok!! =D Here it is people! cs_school_beta This is the beta, as I want to let it out to the public, after a lot of people asking me to do so, so here it is! Notes about beta: Come with ALL the improovements you can! Because I want the final version to be as great as possible!!
Features: -4 hostages. -buyzone. -18 spawns to each team. -HDR -Sounds -Custom model (one only :P) -Nav file -Hours of fun!
Authors: Map: TwixyTwix Models (The base, UVmap, textures): moH Model compile + colousion model: sgt_kick_ur_ass All files ARE INLUDED in the .rar file. PM me if you dont have winrar, and want the .ZIP version If you like it, favourite it then!! To show your support (And/or love for the map)!
